            "text": "UI-DESIGN & OTHER"
          },
          {
            "articleText": "article__text--second",
            "text": "My interest in user interface design comes from my personal passion for art and design."
          },
          {
            "articleText": "article__text--second",
            "text": "Often, a client who wants to create a website expects comprehensive work, not only to design what the website should contain, but also to design the user's interface. Knowledge of such tools as Gimp, Inkscape and Figma allow to realize these expectations."
          },
          {
            "articleText": "article__text--second",
            "text": "Below I present selected projects, such as: UI of websites, icons and logos, graphic design (eg. book covers, infographics) as well as my art activities (paintings and drawings)."
          }
        ]
