          },
          {
            "articleText": "article__text--second",
            "text": "My interest in applied graphics results from my artistic experience, which I have been running since my youth. I mainly do acrylic painting, but also drawing. I had several individual exhibitions (in Elbląg and Gdańsk), as well as collective exhibitions (e.g. in Duseldorf in 2009, at Galeria El - 'Salon Elbląski' in 2009, 2011, 2013). I was also a co-founder of Klaster Biznesu Kultury 'BizArt' (Business of Culture Cluster), which was established on May 11, 2011 in Elbląg."
          },
